{"id":46780,"date":"2024-01-30T09:42:00","date_gmt":"2023-06-30T09:42:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=46780"},"modified":"2023-07-02T18:58:53","modified_gmt":"2023-07-02T13:28:53","slug":"wash-basin-mirror-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/wash-basin-mirror-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Elevate The Style Quotient With 8 Stunning Wash Basin Mirror Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>8 washbasin mirror designs for your home<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A wash basin area is a necessity for every household, be it a corner in your dining space or a part of the bathroom. You don&#8217;t want it to look like a sore thumb. Decorate this small space to match the overall <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/\">decor of your home<\/a>. One such thing is hanging a decorative mirror. So, here is our top selection of the latest wash basin mirror designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Square Wash Basin Mirror With Copper Frame<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A square mirror with a copper frame is a timeless piece that never goes out of style. But you can certainly make it look more stylish. Take a cue from this image below. We have extended the theme of the home into this corner with a bowl-style wash basin in a similar shade, along with two elegantly-designed wall sconces illuminating the space beautifully. Additionally, the traditional Indian-style wooden cupboard adds ample storage space, ensuring practicality and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184713\/square-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg\" alt=\"Square wash basin mirror with a copper frame for a traditional touch\" class=\"wp-image-46789\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184713\/square-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184713\/square-wash-basin-mirror-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184713\/square-wash-basin-mirror-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184713\/square-wash-basin-mirror-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Traditional wash basin cabinet with mirror designs\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Round Wash Basin Mirror Glass Design With Black Leather Strap Hanger<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for ways to transform a boring wash basin nook with something edgy? Try a leather strap to hang it. The round black metal-framed mirror goes amazingly well with this home&#8217;s overall industrial <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184707\/round-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg\" alt=\"Wash Basin Mirror Glass Design in round shape with black strap hanger\" class=\"wp-image-46788\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184707\/round-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184707\/round-wash-basin-mirror-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184707\/round-wash-basin-mirror-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184707\/round-wash-basin-mirror-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Edgy black metal-framed mirror with leather strap<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Minimalist Thin-rimmed Wash Basin Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimalist design doesn&#8217;t have to stop at the living room. Extend it to your wash basin area to match the overall vibe of your home. A simple, square, white wash basin installed on a floating two-tiered cabinet, paired with a large mirror and matching gold faucet, can add to the elegance of your dining space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184700\/thin-rimmed-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg\" alt=\"Thin-rimmed wash basin mirror design for a minimalistic look\" class=\"wp-image-46787\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184700\/thin-rimmed-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184700\/thin-rimmed-wash-basin-mirror-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184700\/thin-rimmed-wash-basin-mirror-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184700\/thin-rimmed-wash-basin-mirror-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Minimalist metal-framed wash basin mirror\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Accent Mirror For Wash Basin Designs\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wash basin mirrors don&#8217;t necessarily have to be boring. Switch your boring old mirror with a heavy accent piece to add vibrancy to your space. It will also work as a decor. Take inspiration from the image below to decorate your space to your heart&#8217;s content.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184356\/accent-mirror-for-wash-basin-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Accent mirror for wash Basin designs to add vibrancy to your space\" class=\"wp-image-46781\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184356\/accent-mirror-for-wash-basin-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184356\/accent-mirror-for-wash-basin-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184356\/accent-mirror-for-wash-basin-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184356\/accent-mirror-for-wash-basin-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Stunning golden mirror for wash basin designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Balance With Sensible Mirror Design On Wash Basin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For a wall-mounted washbasin nook that steals the show with its vibrant colour, pair it with a classic round mirror featuring a simple wooden frame. Its simplicity will surely stand out and also won&#8217;t steal the thunder of the design at the same time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184655\/wooden-framed-mirror-design.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden framed mirror design on wash basin which steals the show\" class=\"wp-image-46786\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184655\/wooden-framed-mirror-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184655\/wooden-framed-mirror-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184655\/wooden-framed-mirror-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184655\/wooden-framed-mirror-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Classic glass wash basin with wooden-framed mirror <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Make A Statement With a Sleek &amp; Modern Wash Basin Mirror Glass Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Why settle for a plain and boring wash basin nook when your interior is all about bold choices? Take inspiration from this black wash basin nook. The sleek round mirror perfectly compliments the stylish wall sconces and bold red oval wash basin. Let your interior do the talking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184417\/modern-wash-basin-mirror-glass-design.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek &amp; modern wash basin mirror glass design to make a statement\" class=\"wp-image-46784\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184417\/modern-wash-basin-mirror-glass-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184417\/modern-wash-basin-mirror-glass-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184417\/modern-wash-basin-mirror-glass-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184417\/modern-wash-basin-mirror-glass-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Make a bold statement with a stylish wash basin mirror<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Revel In The Stylish Appeal Of Unusually-shaped Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you feel rectangle, square and round-shaped mirrors are too mainstream, try mixing the shapes to create something unique. Something like the wash basin mirror shown in the image below. It&#8217;s sure to attract every guest&#8217;s attention.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184411\/unusually-shaped-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg\" alt=\"Unusually-shaped wash basin mirror design for an unique look\" class=\"wp-image-46783\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184411\/unusually-shaped-wash-basin-mirror-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184411\/unusually-shaped-wash-basin-mirror-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184411\/unusually-shaped-wash-basin-mirror-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184411\/unusually-shaped-wash-basin-mirror-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Uniquely shaped wash basin mirror design\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Design your bathroom with our end to end home interior solutions\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/06115036\/design-your-bathroom-with-our-end-to-end-home-interior-solutions-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Rectangle Medicine Cabinet Mirror For Wash Basin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rectangle medicine cabinet mirror is the perfect addition to your wash basin area. With ample space to store your essentials, this mirror not only looks stylish but is also practical. Its sleek design and sturdy construction make it a durable and functional choice for any modern home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184404\/medicine-cabinet-mirror-for-wash-basin.jpg\" alt=\"Medicine cabinet mirror for wash basin which is functional and durable\" class=\"wp-image-46782\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184404\/medicine-cabinet-mirror-for-wash-basin.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184404\/medicine-cabinet-mirror-for-wash-basin-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184404\/medicine-cabinet-mirror-for-wash-basin-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/02184404\/medicine-cabinet-mirror-for-wash-basin-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Hide essentials in plain sight with a medicine cabinet mirror\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, a wash basin mirror is crucial to any <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/modern-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">modern bathroom<\/a> or dining space. From minimalist designs to accent mirrors, there are a plethora of options to choose from to match your style and decor. Pick your style and up your decor game. Should you need help selecting the best mirror design for a wash basin for your home, feel free to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">book a complimentary consultation<\/a> with our senior interior experts. For more such home interior inspirations, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\">blog section<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Wash Basin Mirror Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I choose the right size of the mirror for my wash basin?<\/strong><br>You should consider the size (width &amp; height) of the mirror depending on the width of your vanity. A good way to start is to choose a mirror that is a few inches shorter in width than your countertop and approx 30 inches tall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What is the ideal placement for a wash basin mirror?<\/strong><br>If you have a standalone mirror, ideally, hang it 5-10 inches above the top of the faucet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I clean and maintain my wash basin mirror?<\/strong><br>If you have a stain on your mirror, use rubbing alcohol and a cotton pad to wipe it or use toothpaste. For regular cleaning, spray vinegar and water solution and wipe it with a microfiber cloth.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What safety measures should I keep in mind while installing a wash basin mirror?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Avoid installing a large faucet on a platform with a shallow-bottomed wash basin, as it may overflow the sink.<\/li><li>The distance between the centre of the mirror and the ground should be 5.20-5.40 feet.<\/li><li>If you opt for glass glue for installing your wash basin mirror, avoid acid-based glass glue, as it can adversely affect the mirror.<\/li><li>If installing a mirror for your bathroom wash basin, choose the anti-fog variant.<\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Design your personal oasis of comfort<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n         